title: Geoffrey Keezer - Introduction to Reharmonization (Preview)
description: Available at: https://openstudionetwork.com/keezer - The key to creating good reharmonization (substitute chords) lies in understanding the relationship - bridging the gap - between root movement and the melody line. Without bogging you down with theory, Geoffrey shows you simple and effective tools to give your reharms a boost! Great for guitarists too. (Level: Intermediate)
